                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7972" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1585 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">让“绿色”出圈—大容山生态旅游探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Let the &quot;green&quot; out of the circle- -the innovation road of Darong Mountain ecological tourism product </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林轶，曹清芳，王博</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西乐源大容山文化旅游投资有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西乐源大容山 ；生态旅游 ；E-RMP理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Da Rong Mountain Scenic Area ；ecotourism ；E-RMP theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西乐源大容山景区的前身为大容山林场，于世纪初批准成为国家森林公园，自此旅游资源开发建设突飞猛进。自2015年底广西乐源大容山文化旅游投资有限公司（以下简称乐源文旅投）接手之后，大容山的发展也进入了快车道。天有不测风云，新冠疫情的反复重创了整个旅游行业，同时疫情环境下大批同质化景点景区日趋“内卷”。如今，疫情的阴霾已渐渐散去，众行业开始复苏。但疫情后劲作用下的经济大环境仍不容乐观，游客对景区的品质要求越来越严苛，对大容山来说，是危机同样也是机遇，如何利用自身优势以及相关政策突出重围是目前亟需解决的问题。案例通过聚焦大容山“生态旅游”的探索，从近年越来越受关注的“绿色”视角出发，让学生掌握如何利用E-RMP理论从资源、市场、产品三个维度分析企业现状，重点阐述了大容山如何基于外部环境和自身运营基础，以品牌战略为目标、以生态旅游产品为重点，以绿色营销策略为举措，从而实现观光类旅游发展成为生态旅游的过程，从而在瞬息万变的时代背景和同类竞争越发激烈的情况下为景区生态旅游构建发展提供思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Darong Mountain Scenic Spot in Leyuan, Guangxi, formerly known as Dairong Mountain Farm, was approved as a national forest park in the early century. Since then, the development and construction of tourism resources have made rapid progress. Since the end of 2015, Guangxi Leyuan Darong Mountain Cultural Tourism Investment Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as Leyuan Cultural Tourism Investment) took over, the development of Darong Mountain has entered a fast lane. The repeated outbreak of COVID-19 has hit the entire tourism industry hard. Meanwhile, a large number of homogeneous scenic spots are increasingly &quot;trapped&quot; under the epidemic environment. Now, the shadow of the epidemic has gradually lifted, and industries are starting to recover. However, the economic environment under the effect of the post-epidemic situation is still not optimistic, and tourists have increasingly strict requirements for the quality of the scenic spot. For Darong Mountain, it is both a crisis and an opportunity. How to make use of its own advantages and relevant policies to highlight the surrounding area is an urgent problem to be solved. By focusing on the exploration of &quot;eco-tourism&quot; in Darong Mountain and starting from the perspective of &quot;green&quot;, which has attracted more and more attention in recent years, the case enables students to master how to use E-RMP theory to analyze the current situation of enterprises from three dimensions of resources, market and products, and focuses on how Darong Mountain takes brand strategy as the target and eco-tourism products as the focus based on the external environment and its own operational basis. Green marketing strategy is adopted to realize the process of transforming sightseeing tourism into ecological tourism, so as to provide ideas for the construction and development of ecological tourism in scenic spots under the rapidly changing background and increasingly fierce competition.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生态旅游》、《旅游企业战略管理》、《旅游规划与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌战略；E-RMP理论；绿色营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
